cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.NE, cs.SI. 

The paper discusses a new approach to classification and visualization of continuous data, which is a common problem in machine learning and data mining. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DM (Data Mining). The use of self-organizing maps and stigmergic ant systems also suggests a possible fit with cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
